text:
Might be crawl budget, might be internal links

Sometimes, I see this when Google has discovered the content, but has decided it isn’t relevant enough to index.

I’m assuming you’re targeting the keyword `best paper planners` . If so, check out the content ranking in the top ~20 for that keyword. See if this content looks better than what’s already out there.
